title: 104 Legacy Shorts
description:
MATERIAL: 100% Polyester.

FIT: Fitted.

DESIGN: The Legacy short shorts are made from polyester mesh fabric, perfect for intense workouts. Features include secured elastic waistband with metal tip drawcords, 2 sides, 1 hidden back pocket, and YoungLA flocked print logo.

MODEL: The model in the second photo is wearing a size Medium. Weight: 175lb Height: 5'11.
